Hello,
It seems that reboots (using KDB's 'reboot' or 'reboot -n -f') simply 
hang in machine_emergency_restart() with the x86_64 port on Intel.
On AMD the same kernel reboots perfectly.
I've tried reboot=t - didn't work.
